history.content:
Interested in learning more about machine learning and data science at Accenture? Join DiversaTech this Thursday (October 7th) at 6 PM for a Tech Talk with Accenture Applied Intelligence, whose unique approach to scaling data, analytics and automation is powering every person, in every industry and in every function. They combine the power of disciplines like business strategy with skills like deep machine learning, data science and data architecture and engineering to create innovative solutions.

Accenture's representatives are looking forward to meeting you and answering your questions about their company, culture, and career opportunities with Accenture Consulting and Accenture Technology!

 

Check out the Facebook event page here for the meeting link and to get more information.
